<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Subscribe to Our Newsletter</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .button {
            background-color: #f97316;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #fa8a39;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Stay Updated!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Thank you for your interest in staying updated with our latest news and offers. Click the button below to
                subscribe to our newsletter:</p>
        </div>
        <div class="button-container">
            <a href="{{subscribeUrl}}" class="button">Subscribe</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you did not request this email, please ignore it.</p>
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>University</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>